    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates NIH prediction error within 15% across all five COU-relevant operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied for worst-case operating condition. The assessment team concludes the model has sufficient credibility for the stated COU.",
